Package: DBAbstractR
Type: Package
Title: Database Abstracter
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Pedro", "Moreira", email = "pedromiguelfmoreira@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Pedro Moreira <pedromiguelfmoreira@gmail.com>
Description:
    This package attempts to create a layer of abstraction between its user and the database.
    With minimal notion of relational databases and no notions of SQL at all, you are able to
    transform the information contained in databases to datasets or single tables (Views).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    RODBC (>= 1.3-1.4),
Imports:
    R6 (>= 2.2.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/PedroMiguelFMoreira/DBAbstractR
BugReports: https://github.com/PedroMiguelFMoreira/DBAbstractR/issues
Collate: 
    'SQLQueryFactory.R'
    'DBAbstractR.R'
    'Database.R'
    'DatabaseCredentials.R'
    'SQLQuery.R'
Suggests: testthat
